    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented justifications. Validation metric u_val = 0.09 is below the 0.15 threshold. GCI of 2.1% confirms adequate numerical accuracy. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device per the RH < 1 acceptance criterion.",
